query:
INSERT INTO mirrors_v2
                (host, port, path)
                VALUES
                (?, ?, ?)
                ON CONFLICT
                DO UPDATE SET last_seen = unixepoch(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);

                INSERT INTO deliveries
                (mirror_id, debname, size, duration, partial, client_ip)
                VALUES
                ((SELECT id FROM mirrors_v2 WHERE host = ? AND port = ? AND path = ?), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?);
